ctflags version 0.03
====================

This module allows to set Perl constants from environment variables or
from command line options.

the initial objetive of this module was to allow to mimic from Perl the so common C
debug macros that allow to conditionally compile or leave alone pieces
of code at compile time (actually ctflags stands for compile time
flags).


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module does not require any other module.


